{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-jsx","path":"/google-auth-firebase/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"joy.blog"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"62aaa38c-dc50-56f0-a142-f0be31eb8eee","excerpt":"🎉 firebase 프로젝트 생성 Firebase 에 접속하여 새로운 프로젝트를 생성합니다. 👉 Firebase 바로가기 프로젝트 이름을 입력합니다. Analytics가 필요하지 않으면 OFF 프로젝트에 해당하는 앱을 추가합니다. (ios / android / web) 먼저 1)앱 이름을 정하고 2)생성되는 config 코드를 복사합니다. (프로젝트 배포…","html":"<h2>🎉 firebase 프로젝트 생성</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>Firebase 에 접속하여 새로운 프로젝트를 생성합니다. 👉 <a href=\"https://console.firebase.google.com/u/1/\">Firebase 바로가기</a></li>\n</ol>\n<img src='https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/68415905/158337784-a2053611-e4c2-47f1-9ea8-6a6a3f9d6448.jpg' width='600'>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li>프로젝트 이름을 입력합니다.</li>\n</ol>\n<img src='https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/68415905/158343612-0438483d-57db-400e-9d7c-eec6deb1c908.JPG' width='600'>\n<ol start=\"3\">\n<li>Analytics가 필요하지 않으면 OFF</li>\n</ol>\n<img src='https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/68415905/158343614-06dea897-3dbf-41f7-b94f-179b828739e1.JPG' width='600'>\n<ol start=\"4\">\n<li>프로젝트에 해당하는 앱을 추가합니다. (ios / android / web)</li>\n</ol>\n<img src='https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/68415905/158344954-bbac48bd-a10e-4c39-bf5f-d5722dcd9752.JPG' width='600'>\n<ol start=\"5\">\n<li>먼저 1)앱 이름을 정하고 2)생성되는 config 코드를 복사합니다. <br/>(프로젝트 배포도 함께 원하는 경우 옵션 체크)</li>\n</ol>\n<img src='https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/68415905/158344599-8465cce0-43dc-454c-bf16-f2a296469b28.JPG' width='600'>\n<h2>🙍 Authentication 설정</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>Authentication 섹션에 접속하여 로그인 방법(sign-in method)을 선택합니다.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><img src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/68415905/158357869-3d4ee65a-19c2-4cab-819b-0fdbb46eb859.JPG\" alt=\"fb4\">\n<img src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/68415905/158358729-9deccf70-342f-4d05-a9d0-d86e2354ebdc.JPG\" alt=\"fb5\"></p>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li>로그인 방법으로 <strong>Google</strong>을 선택한 후 이메일을 추가합니다.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><img src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/68415905/158359051-be6288b6-151d-4319-a31b-3b6acae3788a.JPG\" alt=\"fb3\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/68415905/158359382-7092d37f-5e43-465c-879a-1ce5f99af612.JPG\" alt=\"fb1\"></p>\n<h2>🔀 firebase 프로젝트 연동</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>firebase 설치합니다</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">npm</span> <span class=\"token function\">install</span> firebase</code></pre></div>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">firebase.js</code> 파일을 생성한 후 복사한 config 코드를 붙여넣기 합니다.</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> firebase <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"firebase/app\"</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"firebase/auth\"</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> firebaseConfig <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\">// copy and paste</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> app <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> firebase<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">initializeApp</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>firebaseConfig<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">default</span> app<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">auth</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<ol start=\"3\">\n<li>login 컴포넌트에 provider를 추가합니다.</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"jsx\"><pre class=\"language-jsx\"><code class=\"language-jsx\"><span class=\"token comment\">// LoginPage.js</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> firebase <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"firebase/app\"</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> auth <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"../../firebase\"</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> provider <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">GoogleAuthProvider</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token function-variable function\">LoginButton</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>button</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">onClick</span><span class=\"token script language-javascript\"><span class=\"token script-punctuation punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token function\">signInWithPopup</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>auth<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> provider<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">로그인</span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>button</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<ol start=\"4\">\n<li>로그인 실행 시 아래와 같은 로그인 popup창이 생깁니다.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><img src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/68415905/158363860-38723771-32ae-4637-a856-887180b118c5.JPG\" alt=\"fb1\">\n<img src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/68415905/158363958-b206f96f-f441-46d6-b9b8-b4ca8d82bd6e.jpg\" alt=\"fb\"></p>\n<ol start=\"5\">\n<li>로그인에 성공하면 firebase > Authentication > Users에 이메일이 추가됩니다.</li>\n</ol>\n<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>\n<p>REFERENCE<br /> React에서 Firebase Auth를 사용한 로그인 구글 로그인 구현 <a href=\"https://koras02.tistory.com/58\">https://koras02.tistory.com/58</a></p>\n</blockquote>","frontmatter":{"title":"구글 로그인 기능 with Firebase","date":"March 17, 2022","update":"March 17, 2022","tags":["firebase","auth"],"series":"OAuth Service"},"fields":{"slug":"/google-auth-firebase/","readingTime":{"minutes":1.95}}},"seriesList":{"edges":[{"node":{"id":"e24f53d2-1764-5294-bb52-1cb29e4d5a51","fields":{"slug":"/about-auth/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"OAuth 2.0 의 개념 및 용어 정리"}}},{"node":{"id":"71b09413-ac66-5e66-ada6-57a2f2f8ad09","fields":{"slug":"/auth-flow/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"OAuth 2.0 흐름 파악하기"}}},{"node":{"id":"0b2ed25f-d34f-5068-875c-a9afc3edbfe9","fields":{"slug":"/google-auth-clientid/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Google OAuth Client ID 만들기"}}},{"node":{"id":"62aaa38c-dc50-56f0-a142-f0be31eb8eee","fields":{"slug":"/google-auth-firebase/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"구글 로그인 기능 with Firebase"}}}]},"previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/google-auth-clientid/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Google OAuth Client ID 만들기"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/about-socket/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Socket 통신의 특징 및 프로토콜의 종류"}}},"pageContext":{"id":"62aaa38c-dc50-56f0-a142-f0be31eb8eee","series":"OAuth Service","previousPostId":"0b2ed25f-d34f-5068-875c-a9afc3edbfe9","nextPostId":"49a402f3-16dd-5415-9a9e-67cb79026828"}},"staticQueryHashes":[]}